{"tid":2390811,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"試當真投共實情極浪漫！豪哥(蘇致豪)幫TVB拍MV秘辛導讀！(反社會黃衛兵人型炸彈接受唔到人間有愛勿入！) 文:轟焦凍凍","createTime":"2021-02-01T22:27:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T12:27:15.000Z","uid":388757,"like":38,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d8a5ccef72e133cf71ff5a38bbe0a81f19c7c8f8","tid":2390811,"uid":388757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T22:27:20.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"teal\">本帖文由會員轟焦凍凍（已被bam)授權轉載</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到黃衛兵蠢蠢欲動想捉住豪哥去TVB拍MV一事反試當真...<br />\n<br />\n但係你班黃衛兵唔好柒啦... <br />\n<br />\n試當真呢D有實力既youtube channel點會係你班連登社會垃圾反得郁<br />\n<br />\n你地想反，班黃絲都唔撚同你地癲啦...<br />\n<br />\n上次收左達哥皮，班正常黃絲都不知幾撚後悔...<br />\n<br />\n而家焗撚住要睇埋大J D無鳩聊VLOG... <br />\n<br />\n同佢個黃面婆生活無鳩聊 去下CAMP都剪成廿分鐘<br />\n<br />\n為左支持黃channel焗睇... <br />\n<br />\n仲要比個大J以為自己眾星拱月係黃營之首...<br />\n<br />\n出撚埋D 900蚊hoodie...<br />\n<br />\n我地黃絲硬食大J呢件用小學生做target audience既廢中真係慘撚過食屎...<br />\n<br />\n仲要為左支持黃營like埋大J個page <br />\n<br />\n焗住日日睇住佢係facebook(無計啦 mewe都唔多人用 唯有用返facebook 一步一步黎)出埋d低級趣味又唔撚好笑懶係幽默觸覺又慢幾拍既post...<br />\n<br />\n無左風趣幽默既達哥... 無左生活多姿多彩既ming仔...<br />\n<br />\n真係唔想連咁高質既試當真都比黃衛兵批鬥埋...<br />\n<br />\n但係TVB單野又真係唔識點駁黃衛兵....<br />\n<br />\n所以今日凍哥為左各位正常黃絲(非黃衛兵)既利益著想...<br />\n<br />\n決定比大家一個大義凜然既理由支持豪哥而唔比人話雙重標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QI9exwJkHHE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQI9exwJkHHE&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl3s01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=2138780a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QI9exwJkHHE</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/e112baee25218cf94fc24897188764ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2Fe112baee25218cf94fc24897188764ee.jpg&h=1ef65131&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/0a893e42f016419bdd0b46e3cdcc877a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2F0a893e42f016419bdd0b46e3cdcc877a.jpg&h=1c60c0cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/6bbcfd9eb1bea166d0ca59f65cf327b0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2F6bbcfd9eb1bea166d0ca59f65cf327b0.png&h=5db76980&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/a818f5f5092abc0b934ad8bb4bbd399a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2Fa818f5f5092abc0b934ad8bb4bbd399a.jpg&h=e2b45788&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/99c921b96f160eb0f03edd17b6e2b034.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2F99c921b96f160eb0f03edd17b6e2b034.jpg&h=4a169afe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/04117087cb4c9a418cb72ca259e016ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2F04117087cb4c9a418cb72ca259e016ff.jpg&h=3ac06493&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/d063879045483a1add6bc01e49356fe9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2Fd063879045483a1add6bc01e49356fe9.jpg&h=6273b4ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/6755c15041d487a9dc6f74f003bc04af.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2F6755c15041d487a9dc6f74f003bc04af.png&h=aa699670&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/45a9d17fdeb51453fff61eb2fff211b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2F45a9d17fdeb51453fff61eb2fff211b0.jpg&h=4c514daf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/dd0e8b5dfcb5300d81e084f6e95fede9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2Fdd0e8b5dfcb5300d81e084f6e95fede9.jpg&h=3b93c490&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/9dd067aea7d79926f04331661f21a046.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2F9dd067aea7d79926f04331661f21a046.png&h=1b73be10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/1bbb8931119d328dafc2e297915b94f0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2F1bbb8931119d328dafc2e297915b94f0.png&h=dd3fc845&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/9b028dcefe9201f81f30821a9ef35aa6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2F9b028dcefe9201f81f30821a9ef35aa6.png&h=8df6ab0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/258c7ffeeb61c954e31cb4f3e650115d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2F258c7ffeeb61c954e31cb4f3e650115d.png&h=feec3865&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/5b6f9b121a46cfe73f7bafb3fc67e838.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2F5b6f9b121a46cfe73f7bafb3fc67e838.png&h=f4fcc7b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/318a08ac2113bf344cbb44b9de1ac9c9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2F318a08ac2113bf344cbb44b9de1ac9c9.png&h=d540d929&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再睇埋戴祖儀IG <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/2176d7456e13ed4fd2cc9337414e37b4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2F2176d7456e13ed4fd2cc9337414e37b4.png&h=c4df1248&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">唉... 其實重點唔係藍定黃 </span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">唔係TVB藝人奶唔奶共</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">戴祖儀為左借用豪哥幾個鐘扮下情侶煮飯仔 要游說埋星夢高層</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">其實只係一對兩小無猜既戀人 係一個兩極既香港 係呢個又有紅衛兵又有黃衛兵既亂世 想搵一個空間築出佢地愛情既結晶品</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再加上條女咁主動....<br />\n<br />\n戴祖儀素有香港神宮寺(陳到)既美譽 我唔覺得豪哥作為香港渡部建會忍到<br />\n<img src=\"https://i20.tcafe2a.com/1809/20180907015605_0041e83168c56980f62d4b698ad75fdd_1vjg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi20.tcafe2a.com%2F1809%2F20180907015605_0041e83168c56980f62d4b698ad75fdd_1vjg.gif&h=3595ac1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再加上豪哥係我地熱血公民成員，真係反唔落...<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw9AgOjn.jpg&amp;h=eb44d720&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gTaHJVd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgTaHJVd.jpg&h=769015cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kGrGZty.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkGrGZty.jpg&h=d1c18a0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d5mcqUB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd5mcqUB.jpg&h=efa45806&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AOQ41sX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAOQ41sX.jpg&h=e4443659&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5379b99ab163c2563b79b551d2bdfa843bdc243","tid":2390811,"uid":155246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T22:36:10.000Z","msg":"我淨係留意到todoroki<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc0db41b5ca57ab45e98523ee9925c81adb8714b","tid":2390811,"uid":388757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b5379b99ab163c2563b79b551d2bdfa843bdc243","tid":2390811,"uid":1552